## 🚀 Getting Started Locally

If you want to run this project locally:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/adekore1/miniarchi.git
cd miniarchi
npm install
Then, add your OpenAI key in .env.local:

ini
Copy code
OPENAI_API_KEY=your-api-key-here
Start the dev server:

bash
Copy code
npm run dev
Visit http://localhost:3000 in your browser.

🌍 Deploying to the Web
The app is designed for one-click deployment on Vercel:

Fork or clone this repo

Push to your GitHub

Import into Vercel

Set OPENAI_API_KEY in your Vercel environment variables

Deploy and share your live site

